# Distribution of anime types
Let's have a look at the data. How much percentage does each anime type have of all entries.

msg.data:
Distribution of anime types

Let’s have a look at the data. How much percentage does each anime type have of all entries.

paragraphs.text:
%groovy
import groovy.json.JsonSlurper

def offlineDatabase = new JsonSlurper().parse(new File("anime-offline-database.json"))
def resultString = offlineDatabase.data
    .countBy { it.type }
    .collect { "${it.key}\t${it.value}" }
    .join('\n')

print("""%table
type\tamount
$resultString
""")
